<article class="page-container">
	<form  class="form form-horizontal" id="form-academic-add">

        <input type="hidden" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="acadId" name="acadId">

        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>论文名称：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="thesisName" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>刊物名称：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="novon" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>发行代码：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="releasingCode" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>刊物级别：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="publicationLevel" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>刊期：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="periodical" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>收录情况：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text"  class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="collectionSituation" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3"><span class="c-red">*</span>发表刊物：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <input type="text" class="input-text" value="" placeholder="" id="publishJournals" name="username">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
        <label class="form-label col-xs-3">作者排名：</label>
        <div class="formControls skin-minimal col-xs-5">
            <div class="radio-box">
                <input type="radio" id="rank1" name="rank">
                <label for="rank1">第一</label>
            </div>
            <div class="radio-box">
                <input type="radio" id="rank2" name="rank">
                <label for="rank2">第二</label>
            </div>
            <div class="radio-box">
                <input type="radio" id="sex-3" name="rank">
                <label for="rank3">第三</label>
            </div>
            <div class="radio-box">
                <input type="radio" id="rank4" name="rank">
                <label for="sex-4">第四</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-3">类别：</label>
            <div class="formControls skin-minimal col-xs-5">
                <div class="radio-box">
                    <input type="radio" id="cat1" name="category">
                    <label for="cat1">教学</label>
                </div>
                <div class="radio-box">
                    <input type="radio" id="cat2" name="category">
                    <label for="cat1">科研</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3">证明附件：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9"> <span class="btn-upload form-group">
				<input class="input-text upload-url" type="text" name="uploadfile" id="uploadfile" readonly nullmsg="请添加附件！" style="width:200px">
				<a href="javascript:void();" class="btn btn-primary radius upload-btn"><i class="Hui-iconfont">&#xe642;</i> 浏览文件</a>
				<input type="file" multiple id="file" name="file" class="input-file">
				</span>
			</div>
        </div>
        <input type="hidden" value="" id="fileId">
        <div class="row cl">
            <label class="form-label col-xs-4 col-sm-3">注意：</label>
            <div class="formControls col-xs-8 col-sm-9">
                <span class="btn-upload form-group">
                    <p>不重新上传默认用上一次提交的附件。重新上传则覆盖</p>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row cl">
            <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-9 col-xs-offset-4 col-sm-offset-3">
                <input class="btn btn-primary radius" id="submit" type="button" value="&nbsp;&nbsp;修改&nbsp;&nbsp;">
